msgid "NumPy for MATLAB users"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../user/numpy-for-matlab-users.rst:8
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../user/numpy-for-matlab-users.rst:10
msgid ""
"MATLAB® and NumPy have a lot in common, but NumPy was created to work with "
"Python, not to be a MATLAB clone.  This guide will help MATLAB users get "
"started with NumPy."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../user/numpy-for-matlab-users.rst:14
